value.0: Who are you, fool? Don't you know not to go bothering a Bloodsailor while he's drinking?
Hemmel-who? Oh, that fancy pants noble. Damn fool actually believed I could ship them off in a boat. Ha!
Well I ain't giving it up so easy. Hows about a drinking contest for it?
I thought so. All bluff and no stuff. Come back when you've got a spine.
You bet you will, but deep pockets don't get you much here. We respect strength. Can you go drink for drink or not?!
<StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> Heh, you think you scare me, milk drinker? Don't do something you'll regret. Now, the offer is still stands. Drink up and best me or go home.
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start> There's no need to get violent! Here, take the damn amulet. Now leave me be.
All right then! Let's start off with a little Neverwintan Sailor Spirit. A bathtub special here at the Seedy Tavern. Go!
I thought so. All bluff and no stuff. Come back when you've got a spine.
<StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> Ha! Down after one! What kind of <man/woman> are you? Pathetic. You just aren't worthy of my time.
Now take a walk, fool. I'm sure there's some porcelain for you to kiss around here somewhere.
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start> Ah, that's pretty good. You're not so flimsy after all. How about some Dockside Dunn's, a rank bit of swill if I ever had some!
<StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> Eh, should'a sat down when you had the chance. You just aren't up to snuff, as far as I'm concerned.
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start> Whoa! All right! That's not too bad. Round three then! Orc Blood Brew, and no plugging your nose!
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start> All right, but now it gets tough! How about... a little Dwarven Red Eye! It'll make you feel like you're under a pile of stone!
<StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> Well, I guess you should have sat down. Still, you've proven yourself to me. Everything after Dwarven Red Eye was just to see how crazy you are.
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start> Well how about that! You got it down! If you can guzzle drinks down like that, go ahead and take the amulet. Haha!
Now, how about some... oh... Thayvian Fire Juice? Burns in ways you don't want to know! Are you crazy enough to play?!
Yeah, I think you've proven yourself to me. I mean, everything after the Dwarven Red Eye was just to see how crazy you are.
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start> Well I'll be a... How about that?! So... you want to keep going with some... Catoblepas Death Cheese Wine?! Or have you had enough?
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start> Well... looks like we're getting... serious. All right then, from the bowels of the earth, a downright poisonous brew... Dark Elven T'Keela.
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start> Okay... Not that I'm queasy... but do you want to quit... or try a... a Screaming Harpy! You can't imagine... the horror...
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start> Oh hell... okay... you want to play games... *hic*... okay... The meanest... the foulest... black bile of the earth... A bottle... of Scurrd.
<StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> Heh... I knew you couldn't... uh...
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start> Son of a...
I'll leave you to your drinking, then.
Are you Jalek? You should give back Hemmel's amulet.
I don't have time for this foolishness.
I just really need the amulet. I'll gladly pay.
<StartCheck>[Intimidate]</Start> How about you give me the amulet before you end up bloodied and bruised?
Fine. I'll match you drink for drink, no problem!
Ehh, I've changed my mind.
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> Bottoms up!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> Bring it on!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> No problem at all!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> Cheers!
Thanks. Maybe I'll just sit down for a bit, now.
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> I am just fine! Swig it back!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> I am just fine! Swig it back!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> You're not stopping are you? Swig it!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> Bah! Nothing but water! Tip it back!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> Through the lips and over the gums!
